<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.8">
<l>aṉṟiya vāṇa ṉāyiran tōḷun tuṇiyavaṉ ṟāḻitoṭ ṭāṉai</l>
<l>miṉtikaḻ kuṭumi vēṅkaṭa malaimēl mēviya vētanal viḷakkai</l>
<l>teṉticait tilata maṉaiyavar nāṅkaic cempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē,</l>
<l>maṉṟatu poliya makiḻntuniṉ ṟāṉai vaṇaṅkināṉ vāḻntoḻin tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having bowed to the one who remains joyously, so the assembly hall</l>
<l>Within the Cempoṉcey Temple in Nāṅkai, it flourishes,</l>
<l rend="indent">its people like a tilaka to the South,</l>
<l>The one who discharged the discus that day</l>
<l rend="indent">to sever the one-thousand arms of wrathful Bāṇa,</l>
<l>The auspicious lamp of the Vedas which dwells on Vēṅkaṭa Mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">lightning lighting [its] peak, living [happily], I was at ease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
